Comment: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:27.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN Start
Comment: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:41.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那珍貴的失物
Comment: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:44.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相識的你撿起
Comment: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交還給我
Comment: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼說來　重要的東西
Comment: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要寫上名字
Comment: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:58.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然會丟失於不知何處
Comment: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:01.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,經常被這樣告誡
Comment: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的錯
