Comment: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨風　來吧手牽手
Comment: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:18.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,於空　配合對方步調
Comment: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出發了
Comment: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:24.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,心之所向
Comment: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:26.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,與你　沒錯　如果與你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯　正因為與你一起
Comment: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:38.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,向著未知的未來
